zh_CN.DialogText: 想了想，或许让邻居欠你一份人情，日后也好过一个冷漠的邻居

en_US.DialogText: After thinking about it, maybe let the neighbor owe you a favor, which will be better than an indifferent neighbor in the future

zh_CN.DialogText: 下次我来找你帮忙的时候你可别拒绝哦。

en_US.DialogText: Next time I come to you for help, don't refuse.

zh_CN.DialogText: 或许这只会让我浪费一天时间，也或许...会对这个末日世界产生一点影响吧

en_US.DialogText: Maybe it will only waste me a day, or maybe Will it have a little impact on this doomsday world
